              "content": "=Write a high-conversion, professional cold email for the client named {{ $json.body.clientName }} offering the service of {{ $json.body.service }}. MY INFORMATION: My name is Jake and my company is jake.co. STRICT RULES: You must start the response directly with 'Subject:'. Do not use any brackets like [Your Name], [Your Company], or [Insert Phone]. Replace all such placeholders with the information I provided. If some information is missing, simply omit that part instead of using a bracket. Do not include any introductory phrases like 'Sure' or 'Here is your draft'. Only provide the final email content in English."
            }
